description:
The Keroro Platoon is on the case!  Vicious space criminal #303 has come down to Earth, and they`re going to track him down.  But what are all these strange rings they keep finding, and are they clues to his true identity?
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Notre but : la Terre ! / Le visiteur de Titar
ケロロ ペコポンにほえろ! であります / タママ ケロン星からの訪問者 であります
